ciscoWanSrmMIB.name: ciscoWanSrmMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of the MIB. The content of this MIB was originally available in CISCO-WAN-AXIPOP-MIB defined using SMIv1. The applicable objects from CISCO-WAN-AXIPOP-MIB are defined using SMIv2 in this MIB. Also the descriptions of some of the objects have been modified.

ciscoWanSrmMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-wanatm@cisco.com
ciscoWanSrmMIB.description: The MIB module for configuration of bulk distribution (de-multiplexing of traffic from higher-bandwidth to lower-bandwidth interfaces). This is used for configuring bulk distribution of T3 interfaces on T1 modules supported in MGX82xx series. Some of the T1 modules are AUSM, FRSM,CESM. This MIB module also contains info. on configuring bulk distribution of SONET interfaces(VT interfaces) on T1 Modules. SRM - Service Resource Module SRME - Service Resource Module Enhanced.

srm3T3CnfGrpTable.name: srm3T3CnfGrpTable
srm3T3CnfGrpTable.description: The SRM 3T3 configuration table, it is the distribution of a T3 line.

srm3T3CnfGrpEntry.name: srm3T3CnfGrpEntry
srm3T3CnfGrpEntry.description: an entry in the T3 configuration table

srmT3LineNum.name: srmT3LineNum
srmT3LineNum.description: Select T3 line number. There is no default value for this object.

srmStartT1LineNum.name: srmStartT1LineNum
srmStartT1LineNum.description: The start T1 number to be affected. There is no default value for this object.

srmT1RowStatus.name: srmT1RowStatus
srmT1RowStatus.description: a command is used to add, delete, or modify one or more DS1 mapping. Default value is delete.

srmTargetSlotNum.name: srmTargetSlotNum
srmTargetSlotNum.description: specify the target slot number to be linked. There is no default value for this object. For MGX8850: SRM01 services slots 1 - 6 and 9 - 14, SRM02 services slots 17 - 22 and 25 - 30 For MGX8220: SYNTAX Integer32 (5 ..14)

srmTargetSlotLineNum.name: srmTargetSlotLineNum
srmTargetSlotLineNum.description: 0 means not assigned. There is no default value for this object.

srmeCnfGrpTable.name: srmeCnfGrpTable
srmeCnfGrpTable.description: The SRME configuration table for bulk distribution of SRME lines.

srmeCnfGrpEntry.name: srmeCnfGrpEntry
srmeCnfGrpEntry.description: an entry in the SRME Distribution configuration table

srmeLineNum.name: srmeLineNum
srmeLineNum.description: This object identifies the SRME line number. For OC3/STM1: SYNTAX Integer32 1 There is no default value for this object.

srmeStartVtNum.name: srmeStartVtNum
srmeStartVtNum.description: The start T1 or E1 number (virtual tributary) to be affected. For OC3 with T1 tributaries: SYNTAX Integer32 (1 .. 84) For STM1 with E1 tributaries: SYNTAX Integer32 (1 .. 63) There is no default value for this object.

srmeRowStatus.name: srmeRowStatus
srmeRowStatus.description: Command used to add, delete, or modify one or more T1 or E1 mappings. Only the srmeVtFramingType object can be modified once the distribution link is added. To modify all other objects, user should first delete the link and add it again. Default value is modify(3).

srmeTargetSlotNum.name: srmeTargetSlotNum
srmeTargetSlotNum.description: This object specifies the target slot number to be linked. There is no default value for this object. For MGX8x50: SRM01 services slots 1 - 6 and 9 - 14, SRM02 services slots 17 - 22 and 25 - 30 For MGX8x30: service slots 3-6 and 10-13.

srmeTargetSlotLineNum.name: srmeTargetSlotLineNum
srmeTargetSlotLineNum.description: Specify the target slot's line to be linked. The value zero means, the target line number is not assigned. There is no default value for this object.

srmeVtFramingType.name: srmeVtFramingType
srmeVtFramingType.description: Specifies the Framing Type of the target slot line. This is applicable only if the target module is a T1 Service Module and byte sync mapping is used on SRME. Not applicable to E1 Service Modules. sf: Superframe or D4 esf: Extended Superframe. Default is 'esf' if SRME lines are configured for byte-synchronous mapping, Else, the default is notApplicable.

ciscoWanSrmCompliance.name: ciscoWanSrmCompliance
ciscoWanSrmCompliance.description: The compliance statement for objects related to SRM MIB.

ciscoWanSrmConfGroup.name: ciscoWanSrmConfGroup
ciscoWanSrmConfGroup.description: The collection of objects which are used for configuring bulk distribution for SRM module.

ciscoWanSrmeConfGroup.name: ciscoWanSrmeConfGroup
ciscoWanSrmeConfGroup.description: The collection of objects which are used for configuring bulk distribution for SRM-E module.
